<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/306941.No_Future"><img alt="No Future: Queer Theory and the Death Drive" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1345701353l/306941._SX98_.jpg" />
